{"title": "Berlin Workshop on Degrowth and Gender", "author": null, "url": "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/research/research-archive/DegrowthandGender/Berlin%20Workshop%20on%20Degrowth%20and%20Gender", "hostname": "hu-berlin.de", "description": null, "sitename": "Thaer-Institut", "date": "2016-01-13", "id": null, "license": null, "body": null, "comments": "", "commentsbody": null, "raw_text": null, "text": "Berlin Workshop on Degrowth and Gender\nThe Berlin Workshop on Degrowth and Gender\n-\nIs a network of Berlin-based international scholars working on Feminist Political Ecology\n-\nIs a think-tank for the exploration of feminist perspectives on degrowth\n-\nWants to encourage radical thinking about economic change\nWe are organizing a one-day workshop with Wendy Harcourt on sustainable livelihoods on 8 April 2016.\nBe part of it!\nThe workshop is directed towards scholars who plan to do their doctoral thesis on degrowth in a feminist economics framework. In order to maintain a personal working atmosphere places in the workshop are limited.\nPlease send your application by 29 February 2016 to\n[berlin.degrowth.gender@hu-berlin.de](mailto:berlin.degrowth.gender@hu-berlin.de)\nYour application should include the description of your research project (500 words maximum) and a letter of motivation.\nWe are looking forward to your application.\nFor more information please contact Prof. Dr. Christine Bauhardt:\n[christine.bauhardt@gender.hu-berlin.de](mailto:christine.bauhardt@gender.hu-berlin.de)\nStudent Symposium\nA good life for all? \u2013 Postwachstum meets Gender\nWith: Dr. Barbara Muraca (OSU), Prof. Dr. G\u00fclay \u00c7a\u011flar (FU Berlin), Prof. Dr. Christine Bauhardt (HU Berlin), Dr. Mike Laufenberg (TU Berlin), Marion Ben Rabah (Projekt \u201eLebensenergie f\u00fcr das Dorf\u201c), sowie weiteren Aktivist_innen aus den Bereichen Care und Food (angefragt)\nModeration& Organisation: Carla Wember (HU), Maren Birkenstock (V\u00d6W), Mike Korsonewski (HU), Sabine Carl (HU), Viktoria Graf (HU)\nWhen? 19.07.2016, 10:00 Uhr \u2013 17:00 Uhr\nWhere? Albrecht Daniel Thaer-Institut f\u00fcr Agrar- und Gartenbau-Wissenschaften, Phillipstr.13, 10115 Berlin\nMore informations:\n[www.postwachstum.de](http://www.postwachstum.de/)", "language": null, "image": "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/@@site-logo/og_logo.png", "pagetype": "website", "links": ["#content", "#search", "#portletNavigationTree", "https://www.hu-berlin.de/", null, "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/@@multilingual-selector/1ec0caa63082448996813060388bfe76/de?set_language=de", "http://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/fakultaet-en/departments/daoe/gg-en", "https://www.hu-berlin.de/", null, "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/sitemap", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/Whats%20new", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/teachings-department", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/npublikationen", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/books", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/research", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/research/researchtopics", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/research/CurrentProjects", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/research/research-archive", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/research/research-archive/hortinlea-en", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/research/research-archive/DegrowthandGender", "https://www.agrar.hu-berlin.de/en/institut-en/departments/daoe/gg-en/research/re